latestPosts.caption:
A lot of people unfortunately, can’t stand up for others, and I think it’s because they “don’t wanna get in trouble” for anybody else’s sake, now while I think that’s wrong, I understand that they’ve been taught that, to think about themselves first, to be selfish if it keeps you out of trouble, because who cares, right ?! 
Well…I’m happy to say that I’m not one of the people who would keep quiet just because the wrong that’s happening is not harming me. Because I would like to believe that everytime I stand up to speak for people who can’t, there would come times in my life when I’ll find people who will dare to speak for me when I am unable to. And even if there aren’t, I’d still feel comforted knowing I did the right thing while I had the chance, no matter the consequence. 
.
Sorry if you expected a normal caption that doesn’t make you THINK.🎀
